Final Exam
Pseudocode
Contact Manager Client List

1. Open app to main page
		display client list
		Links to 3 Action Options
			Add Client
			Edit Client
			Delete Client
			
2. Add Client
		Fields for Name, Email, Phone and Website
		Server Side Validation for form completion, email and phone validity
		Save/Submit
		Add to Database/Show on Website
		Success Message Alert
		Redirect Main Page
		
3.  Edit Client
		All fields will be editable
		Save/Submit Changes
		Add changes to Database/show on website
		Success Message Alert
		Redirect to Main
		
4.  Delete Client
		Filter by ID
		User confirms Deletion
		Delete from List / Database
		Success Message Alert
		Redirect to Main